sentences.english: He was anointed princeps ; the Roman empire is said to begin with his accession.

sentences.english: Leading the effort today are Western-oriented leaders who are almost uniformly young.

sentences.english: As for the word that thou hast spoken unto us in the name of the LORD, we will not hearken unto thee.

sentences.english: Serve the Lord your God, so that his fierce anger will turn away from you.
